• Color Contrast:
o Minimum 4.5:1 ratio for normal text
o Minimum 3:1 ratio for large text
o Focus indicators visible in both themes
o Information not conveyed by color alone
• Adaptable Content:
o Responsive layouts (320px to 1920px+)
o Dynamic Type support (iOS)
o Font scaling support (Android)
o Logical reading order
• Distinguishable:
o Dark mode and light mode support
o System theme detection
o Reduce motion support for animations
o Audio descriptions for video (future)
Operable
• Keyboard Navigation (Web):
o All interactive elements keyboard accessible
o Logical tab order
o Visible focus indicators
o Keyboard shortcuts for common actions
o Skip navigation links
• Touch Targets (Mobile):
o Minimum 44×44 points (iOS)
o Minimum 48×48 dp (Android)
o Adequate spacing between targets
o Large hit areas for small controls
• No Keyboard Trap:
o Users can navigate in and out of all components
o Modal dialogs have proper focus management
• Adjustable Timing:
o No automatic timeouts for critical actions
o Warnings before session expiration
o Ability to extend time limits
Understandable
• Readable:
o Clear, simple language (B1 level German)
o Consistent terminology
