o Variants:
▪ Light: #5AA5F7 (hover states)
▪ Dark: #1A6BC4 (pressed states)
Supporting Colors
• Success Green: #47B881
o Use: Confirmations, completed states, positive feedback
• Warning Orange: #FF8551
o Use: Attention needed, non-critical errors
• Error Red: #E12D39
o Use: Critical errors, destructive actions, validation failures
• Info Purple: #7B68EE
o Use: Informational messages, tips
