Semantic Usage
• Backgrounds: Create depth and hierarchy
• Actions: Primary button color, links, selection
• Feedback: Success/error/warning states
• Text: Hierarchy through contrast
• Borders: Subtle separation and focus
2. Typography
Font Family
• Primary Font: Inter (system: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI")
• Weights: 400 (Regular), 500 (Medium), 600 (Semibold), 700 (Bold), 800 (Extrabold)
• Fallback: System sans-serif
Type Scale (Mobile-first)
• Heading 1: 32px / 700 weight / -0.5px letter-spacing
o Use: Page titles, hero text
• Heading 2: 24px / 700 weight / -0.25px letter-spacing
o Use: Section headers, card titles
• Heading 3: 20px / 600 weight / 0px letter-spacing
o Use: Subsections, important items
• Body Large: 18px / 400 weight / 0px letter-spacing
o Use: Prominent body text, descriptions
• Body Regular: 16px / 400 weight / 0px letter-spacing
o Use: Standard body text, form inputs
• Body Small: 14px / 500 weight / 0px letter-spacing
o Use: Labels, metadata, secondary information
• Caption: 12px / 500 weight / 0.5px letter-spacing
o Use: Tiny labels, legal text, footnotes
Button Text
• Primary/Secondary: 16px / 700 weight / 0.5px letter-spacing / uppercase
• Text Button: 14px / 600 weight / 0px letter-spacing
Line Heights
• Headings: 1.2 (tighter for impact)
• Body text: 1.5 (comfortable reading)
• Captions: 1.4
Text Styling
• Emphasis: Bold weight, not italic
• Links: Primary color, underline on hover (web)
• Disabled: 50% opacity
• Truncation: Ellipsis after max lines (2 for titles, 3 for descriptions)
Responsive Scaling (Tablet/Desktop)
• Heading 1: 48px
• Heading 2: 32px
• Heading 3: 24px
• Body: 18px
• Scale factor: 1.25x
