• Use semantic icons (intuitive meaning)
• Consistent size within same context
• Color: Match text color or primary for actions
• Spacing: 8px padding around icons in buttons
Platform-Specific Icons
• iOS: SF Symbols as backup (native feel)
• Android: Material Icons (platform consistency)
• Web: Material Symbols (consistency with mobile)
4. Spacing & Layout
Spacing Scale (8px base unit)
• XXS: 4px (tight spacing, inline elements)
• XS: 8px (related elements)
• S: 12px (form field vertical spacing)
• M: 16px (card padding, section spacing)
• L: 24px (component separation)
• XL: 32px (major section breaks)
• XXL: 48px (page-level spacing)
Layout Grid
• Mobile: 4-column grid, 16px gutter
• Tablet: 8-column grid, 24px gutter
• Desktop: 12-column grid, 24px gutter
• Max Width: 1440px (centered)
Safe Areas
• iOS: Respect safe area insets (notch, home indicator)
• Android: System bar padding
• Bottom navigation: Padding for gesture areas
Card Layouts
• Padding: 16px (mobile), 24px (tablet+)
• Border Radius: 12px (standard), 16px (large cards)
• Elevation: 0-8dp shadows
• Spacing: 16px between cards
Touch Targets
• Minimum: 44×44pt (iOS), 48×48dp (Android)
• Recommended: 56×56 for primary actions
• Spacing: 8px minimum between targets
5. Elevation & Shadows
Shadow Levels (Material Design inspired)
• Level 0 (Flat): No shadow
o Use: Backgrounds, inline elements
• Level 1 (Subtle): 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.24)
o Use: Cards at rest
• Level 2 (Raised): 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.16), 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.23)
o Use: Raised buttons, hovered cards
• Level 3 (Floating): 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.19), 0 6px 6px
rgba(0,0,0,0.23)
o Use: Modals, dialogs, dropdowns
• Level 4 (Top): 0 14px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.25), 0 10px 10px
rgba(0,0,0,0.22)
o Use: App bar, bottom nav (when scrolling)
• Level 5 (Overlay): 0 19px 38px rgba(0,0,0,0.30), 0 15px 12px
rgba(0,0,0,0.22)
o Use: Full-screen modals, overlays
Dark Mode Shadows
• Reduced opacity (50% of light mode)
• Optional: Elevation via lighter borders instead of shadows
Colored Shadows (Special cases)
• Primary button: 0 4px 12px rgba(37,140,244,0.3)
• Success: 0 4px 12px rgba(71,184,129,0.3)
• Error: 0 4px 12px rgba(225,45,57,0.3)
6. Animation & Motion
Duration Guidelines
• Instant: 100ms (micro-interactions)
• Fast: 200ms (button states, hover)
• Standard: 300ms (screen transitions, modals)
• Slow: 500ms (page transitions, large movements)
Easing Functions
• Ease-out: Default for entrances (cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1))
• Ease-in: Exits (cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1))
• Ease-in-out: Emphasize movement (cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1))
• Spring: iOS-style smooth motion
Animation Types
• Fade: Opacity 0 → 1
• Slide: Transform translateY/X
• Scale: Transform scale 0.95 → 1
• Blur: Backdrop filters
• Skeleton: Shimmer loading animation
Micro-interactions
• Button press: Scale 0.98 (100ms)
• Toggle switch: Slide + color change (200ms)
• Checkbox: Checkmark draw animation (300ms)
• Ripple effect: Expand from tap point (400ms)
• Pull-to-refresh: Spinner rotation
Screen Transitions (Mobile)
• iOS: Default push/pop (slide)
• Android: Material motion (shared element)
• Modal: Slide up from bottom
• Dialog: Fade + scale from center
Reduced Motion
• Respect system preference
• Replace animations with instant transitions
• Keep essential feedback (color changes)
7. Imagery & Media
Image Aspect Ratios
• Event Hero: 16:9 (landscape)
• Activity Thumbnail: 1:1 (square)
• Profile Photo: 1:1 (circular crop)
• Share Preview: 1.91:1 (Open Graph)
Image Optimization
• Format: WebP with JPEG fallback
• Quality: 80% compression
• Responsive: 3 sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)
• Lazy loading: Below fold
• Placeholder: Dominant color or blur
Image States
• Loading: Skeleton with shimmer
• Error: Placeholder with icon
• Empty: Illustration + message
Video (Future)
• Format: MP4 (H.264)
• Poster frame: Preloaded image
• Controls: Native player
• Captions: WebVTT format
Icons & Illustrations
• Format: SVG (vector)
• Style: Line art with selective fills
• Color: Adaptive to theme
• Size: Scalable without quality loss
8. Accessibility Considerations in Design
Color Contrast
• Text on background: 4.5:1 minimum
• Large text: 3:1 minimum
• Interactive elements: 3:1 minimum
• Focus indicators: 3:1 against adjacent colors
Focus Indicators
• Visible outline: 2px solid primary color
• Offset: 2px from element
• Never rely on color alone
Touch Target Sizing
• Interactive elements: 44×44pt minimum
• Spacing: 8px between adjacent targets
• Extend hit area if visual is smaller
Text Sizing
• Respect system font size preferences
• Test at 200% zoom
• No information loss at larger sizes
Motion & Animation
• Respect prefers-reduced-motion
• Essential information without animation
• No auto-playing videos with sound
Alternative Text
• All images have meaningful alt text
• Decorative images: empty alt attribute
• Icons: ARIA labels
